description:
Jorge Aragao - Ao Vivo
1999

Brought to you by TQMP
The Quality Music Project

Chances are if you have ever heard samba, no matter who's singing, you've heard Jorge Aragao's compositions. This record captures the magic of Aragao live. He's a very talented songwriter and can play several string instruments and percussion. It helps if you understand Portuguese, as the lyrics have a beautiful simplicity, but make no mistake - This is rhythm that will touch you, then move you. Literally. If you've never heard samba before you just didn't know how much you love samba. Have fun. Dance. Pretend nobody's watching ;)

Oh, and don't forget His Noodly Appendage.

